Package interfaces.views

package interfaces.views
The interfaces.views contains view interfaces defining the user interface functionalities. Interfaces in this package represent contracts that define how different views should be presented to users.
Since:
1.0
Version:
1.0

  • Interfaces
    Class
    Description
    CampDetailViewable
    The CampDetailViewable interface extends the Viewable interface and is used for displaying detailed information about a camp.
    CampViewable
    The CampViewable interface extends the SortViewable interface and is used for displaying information about camps.
    EnquiryViewable
    The EnquiryViewable interface extends the Viewable interface and is used for displaying information about enquiries.
    ProfileViewable
    The ProfileViewable interface extends the Viewable interface and defines a method for displaying a profile view.
    SortViewable
    The SortViewable interface defines a method for displaying a sorted view of implementing classes based on the specified SortType.
    SuggestionViewable
    The SuggestionViewable interface extends the Viewable interface and is used for displaying information about suggestions.
    Viewable
    The Viewable interface defines a method for displaying the information of implementing classes.
